{
  "title": "ISic002006. Punic funerary inscription",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy De Simone 2025-03-23</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-transliteration\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>qbr <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ḥʿṣ\n                    bn ʿzry\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ḥʿṣ\">ḥ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">...</span>]ʿṣ</span>  <span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span><br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>bn <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ʿzry\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ʿzry\">ʿzry</span></span></span>  <span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span></span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy De Simone 2025-03-23</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-transliteration\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>QBR<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ḥʿṣ\n                    bn ʿzry\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ḥʿṣ\">Ḥ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">···</span>]ʿṢ</span><span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>BN<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ʿzry\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ʿzry\">ʿZRY</span></span></span><span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic002006_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo R. De Simone\" src=\"ISic002006_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic002006.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo R. De Simone\" src=\"ISic002006-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of De Simone from autopys</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7393-1952\">Rossana De Simone</a></p>  <p>Tomb of ḥ[...]ʿṣ, son of ʿzry</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7393-1952\">Rossana De Simone</a></p>  <p>Tomba di ḥ[...]ʿṣ, figlio di ʿzry</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The name of the deceased cannot be reconstructed. ʿ<span class=\"lang\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\">zry</span> is a hypocoristic Phoenician personal name with suffix -y from the root <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\">ʿzr</span> \"to help\". </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Coacci Polselli 1978 163-166 no.1, tav. LXXXV.2 </li><li> De Simone 2013 25 MO.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002545\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002545</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-2  50-108  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
